==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subconscious
<hw>Sub*con"scious</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Occurring without the possibility or the fact of an attendant
consciousness; -- said of states of the soul.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Partially conscious; feebly conscious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subconsciousness</ent>⟦br⟧
